'''马斯伦尼卡大桥'''（{{lang-hr|Most Maslenica}},<ref name="Gradjevinar-MaslenicaD8">{{cite news | newspaper = Građevinar | language = hr | url = http://www.casopis-gradjevinar.hr/dokumenti/200412/5.pdf | title = Reconstruction of the old Maslenica Bridge | date = February 7, 2005 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110718202629/http://www.casopis-gradjevinar.hr/dokumenti/200412/5.pdf | archivedate =2011-07-18}}</ref>，亦称为{{lang-hr|Maslenički most}}）是一座[[拱桥|拱桥]]，坐落在[[克罗地亚|克罗地亚]][[马斯伦尼卡|马斯伦尼卡]]西面1公里，横跨[[亚得里亚海|亚得里亚海]][[马斯利尼察海峡|马斯利尼察海峡]]，[[克罗地亚D8州际公路|克罗地亚D8州际公路]]从桥上通过。

== 结构 ==
马斯伦尼卡大桥长度为315.3m，由一个钢铁铸成的拱支撑混凝土浇筑的桥面，桥面由17个连续的箱式拱组成。<ref name="Gradjevinar-MaslenicaD8"/><ref name="MMPI-2005">{{cite news | newspaper = Ministry of Sea, Transport and Infrastructure (Croatia) | language = hr | url = http://www.mmpi.hr/default.aspx?id=907 | title = Minister Kalmeta opens the Maslenica Bridge across Novsko Ždrilo | date = June 17, 2005}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
最初的马斯伦尼卡大桥于1961年通车。1989年，由于交通繁忙维护不够，桥梁和桥墩出现裂缝，修复工作进行了半年，期间货运停止。1990年大桥再次全面运转。之后再度进行维护，限制流量。<ref name="Gradjevinar-MaslenicaD8"/>

不幸的是，1991年11月21日，[[克罗地亚战争|克罗地亚战争]]期间该桥被摧毁。

2003年开始考虑在原桥基础上重修一座新桥。原桥仅剩下两个桥墩和南面的结构，新设计基本基于原先的设计，只做细微修改。桥的宽度由原先的9.4米增加到10.5米。桥墩和承力柱重新浇筑。大桥于2005年6月17日竣工并重新通车。<ref name="MMPI-2005"/>总计建桥费用为5980万[[克罗地亚库纳|克罗地亚库纳]]。

==名称混淆==
在其北面1.5公里处，也有一座大桥，跨过同一个海峡，A1高速公路从上面通过。尽管是两座不同的桥，通过的公路也不一样，该桥也被称为[[马斯伦尼卡大桥_(A1)|马斯伦尼卡大桥]]。A1高速公路的大桥比现在D8州际公路的桥要老，但是D8州际公路原来的桥在1991年克罗地亚战争期间被摧毁，如今两座桥都被称为“新”“老”“马斯伦尼卡大桥”。<ref name="Nacional-2002">{{cite news | newspaper = Nacional | language = hr | url = http://www.nacional.hr/clanak/13238/povratak-starog-maslenickog-mosta | title = Return of the old Maslenica Bridge | date = October 2, 2002 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/68sVLOdEE?url=http://www.nacional.hr/clanak/13238/povratak-starog-maslenickog-mosta | archivedate = 2012年7月3日 }}</ref><ref name="Gradimo-Maslenica">{{cite news | newspaper = Gradimo.hr | language = hr | url = http://www.gradimo.hr/Otvoren-novi-Maslenicki-most/hr-HR/3089.aspx | title = New Maslenica Bridge opens (taken from Novi List) | date = June 20, 2005 | access-date = 2011-04-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100306174718/http://www.gradimo.hr/Otvoren-novi-Maslenicki-most/hr-HR/3089.aspx | archive-date = 2010-03-06 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name="Vjesnik-2002">{{cite news | newspaper = Vjesnik | language = hr | url = http://www.vjesnik.hr/Pdf/2002%5C10%5C04%5C07A7.PDF | title = New old bridge against wind and congestion | date = October 4, 2002 }}{{dead link|date=十一月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>

